The Agentic RAG for Ukrainian system uses the Qwen2.5-3B-Instruct LLM backbone for generation. This system combines a two-stage retrieval mechanism (BGE-M3 with BGE reranking) with an agentic layer that performs query rephrasing and answer-retry loops. The analysis indicates that while the agentic mechanisms improve answer accuracy, the overall performance is primarily limited by the quality of document and page identification.

